          <h4>How do we report problems within Maintenance and Support plans?</h4>
          <p>You can send a new ticket to <a href="mailto:support@handsontable.com">support@handsontable.com</a>.
            You can also use the form on <a href="//my.handsontable.com" target="_blank">my.handsontable.com</a>.
            We encourage you to visit our forum <a href="//forum.handsontable.com" target="_blank">forum.handsontable.com</a> whenever
            you are stuck. It is the best place to quickly find a solution to your problem and to get in touch with
            other developers.</p>
          <h4>What do I get with the Basic Maintenance and Support plan that comes with the license? </h4>
          <p>With the purchase of a new license you get a Basic Maintenance and Support for 12 months, which gives you:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Minor and patch releases,</li>
            <li>1 hour of support via email (it does not include coding),</li>
            <li>Access to the developers forum at <a href="//forum.handsontable.com" target="_blank">forum.handsontable.com</a>.</li>
          </ul>
          </p>
          <h4>What do I get with the Extended Maintenance and Support plan?</h4>
          <p>Extended Maintenance and Support is an extra service valid for 12 months. It gives you:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Major, minor and patch releases,</li>
            <li>10 hours of support via email, which includes coding, guidance in best practices and also code review,</li>
            <li>Access to the developers forum:
              <a href="//forum.handsontable.com" target="_blank">forum.handsontable.com</a>,</li>
            <li>Possibility to contact directly our core team,</li>
            <li>Initial answer in 12 hours within Handsoncode working hours: 8:00 am - 5:00 pm CET, Monday to
              Friday (local time in Poland).</li>
          </ul>
          <h4>Can I get the Extended Maintenance and Support separately?</h4>
          <p>Yes, that is possible. To do so, please contact our <a href="mailto:sales@handsontable.com">Sales Team.</a></p>
          <h4>Can I buy Maintenance and Support plan only for some of the developers within the license? </h4>
          <p>Our support services are offered for all the developers under the license. You can't, for instance,
            purchase 5 plans of Extended Maintenance and Support if your license is for 10 developers.</p>
          <h4>Do you offer professional consulting and development on demand? </h4>
          <p>Yes, we do. Our services include building apps from scratch, integrating Handsontable with existing
            solutions and optimizing the code.</p>

